  "texts": [
    "This catalog was used to assess the participants' analysis performance.",
    "The maximum possible score resulted from the average depth and complexity of the experts' answers.",
    "The possible number of points per item varied between 1 and 3.",
    "The average score per item was then calculated separately for the experimental and control groups.",
    "In this way, it was possible to determine how close the participants in both groups were to the experts' judgment."
  ],
